'''Tsi''', or '''Mrlsstese''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Mrlssi]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Mrlsst/Legends|Mrlsst]]. Mrlsstese had high piping sounds that some species found delightful and others exasperating. It was considered by some a difficult language to learn.

Most Mrlssi were fluent in both Mrlsstese and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], being literate in both languages. Mrlssi accent when speaking Basic had the same effect in [[Alien/Legends|alien]] audiences than Mrlsstese.

